{"tid":1501847,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"老老實實 係咪應該罷搭港鐵？","createTime":"2019-08-24T13:18:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T13:38:37.000Z","uid":26557,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"347e06a89241a313580769c319de55e1bef62084","tid":1501847,"uid":26557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T13:18:57.000Z","msg":"兩個月嚟 我地整理咗好多罷食名單 大家都有響應<br />\n<br />\n唔知道大家又有冇諗過罷搭港鐵呢？<br />\n<br />\n港鐵作為全香港使用量第一嘅公共交通骨幹 車費年年有加冇減 我地都算<br />\n<br />\n仆你個街 721 811 呢兩件事證明咗港鐵有幾咁無能 冇辦法管理自己嘅站之餘 仲視香港市民生命如草芥 任由黑社會喺站入面打人 任由黑警喺密閉嘅港鐵站內放催淚彈同行刑式槍擊香港市民<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">直至今日 港鐵依然冇正面回應過呢兩日發生嘅事 你地對唔對得住香港市民？</span><br />\n<br />\n今日觀塘遊行更封站阻止香港市民參加遊行<br />\n<br />\n你仲俾錢佢賺？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">即日起 罷搭港鐵 直至港鐵正面回應721 811事件 及譴責黑警濫權執法為止</span><br />\n<br />\n我知道要大家唔搭港鐵係會好唔方便 但我地嘅行動先最有力表達到我地嘅訴求 我地可以罷食吉野家 大家又可以一齊罷搭港鐵嗎？<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc4e8db2201e577fe82d2faa8f97c62a9d8d46a1","tid":1501847,"uid":108337,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T13:19:32.000Z","msg":"跳閘 / 長者八達通 / 小童八達通"},{"pid":"131d18fc82f57febbee997e0f79811efbef43f06","tid":1501847,"uid":20963,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T13:21:14.000Z","msg":"一齊跳閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8a302e015da8fb2d762f339183f31e8de894d31","tid":1501847,"uid":229305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T13:23:02.000Z","msg":"跳"},{"pid":"24543ebce751c47c592ed10348f1760eb9ae609b","tid":1501847,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T13:24:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xqDDOWt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxqDDOWt.png&h=921bbdae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港人<br />\n俾啲骨氣好唔好<br />\n呢頭屌晒鬼<br />\n轉頭又繼續俾錢黨鐵賺</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記住我地先係金主阿！</span></span>"},{"pid":"933a9b5f47a8c21d4a778a2de314714e3e20cf97","tid":1501847,"uid":141493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T13:26:00.000Z","msg":"鐵照搭，唔L俾錢🖕🏻🖕🏻🖕🏻"},{"pid":"9dcc71c3a7237c5b646e476110107b27d1ff91d0","tid":1501847,"uid":26557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T13:32:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3af6db0c4498000ec376bce96fd32db668b61dee","tid":1501847,"uid":76404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"933a9b5f47a8c21d4a778a2de314714e3e20cf97","tid":1501847,"uid":141493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T13:26:00.000Z","msg":"鐵照搭，唔L俾錢🖕🏻🖕🏻🖕🏻"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T13:35:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3a80cc4b212e5cfe3b0da98e36b2d3ed8c54b3a","tid":1501847,"uid":26557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T13:38:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\